Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不來？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這不是很好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Layer:01 WEIRD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼非這樣做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己一定要想清楚……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶你去個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,……即使不在這世界也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與我無關 我什麼也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就再也離不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能靜一點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快一點 走快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉 不要在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯 只是一場惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有事的 茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒收到那東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E-MAIL？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由四方田千砂寄來的E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太會用電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總還得天天查查E-MAIL吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為玲音還是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎麼會哭成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她收到了千砂的E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂的……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D班的同學 上星期在涉谷跳樓自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也提過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只茱莉收到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已有好幾位同學在這個星期也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，她已經……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 死人是不會送E-MAIL的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他們真的收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在她死的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛…(笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LOG IN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 請唸出姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音頻核對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確定 你是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在查閱資料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已接收給玲音的電子郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四方田千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要讀取E-MAIL嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們曾在放學後一同回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我只是拋棄了我的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在另一個空間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才發E-MAIL給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在不明白也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遲早會明白的 大家也都會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要死？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人寫惡作劇E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成謠言散佈在學校中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓你知道那並不是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要死？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡有神的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很晚才吃午餐 我飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了一封E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上個星期自殺的那位同學寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很少來這房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那一部……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那部電腦是新型的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於對它有興趣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音已經是個中學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定比朋友們晚了一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要用更新的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 這個世界是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在真實的世界或是網上的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類都需要交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣世界才會進步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像玲音這樣的小孩子 一定很快就能交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼媽媽總是不明白這道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是怕怎樣 只是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼突然說這些呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個想見面的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位乘客 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列車因事故需要暫停行駛 不便之處 敬請原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？ 有意外嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩倉同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩倉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一題考試會考喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上網來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
